txt.en:
'Welcome warrior. This is your opportunity to prove your prowess on the field of battle. If you choose to, you may speak with me again to enter mortal battle with an opponent of great power and strength.

'You will take on the role of a ranger of Esteldín a noble Man who fights to defend and keep safe the sanctity of Middle-earth. Your opponent will be a terrible troll out of Angmar.

'Speak with me again to launch your ranger session.'
'Ah, then you are prepared to take on the role of noble Man. Very well.'
You have achieved a goal open to only a few. You will have the glory of representing the Free People as a ranger from Esteldín against a troll out of Angmar.
Speak with the ranger to enter mortal battle as a ranger
Speak again to the ranger within this room and choose to enter battle as a noble ranger out of Esteldín.
Speak with the ranger to complete the quest.
Speak with the ranger to complete the quest.
